Suite/Test/Step Name: FCSCMS-193 (Organizations - Client Profile - Add New Client)

Description: Admin user should be able to log in using valid credentials
User should be able to click the Clients option from the left navigation panel
The user can click on the 'Add New Client' button
User can view the name of the client at the title of the page
The user can input or edit details on the 'Basic Information' tab
